name: Petrok
description: The PetRok project is about building a whimsical, carefree community on the Ethereum network, inspired by the legendary adventures of Sir PetRok the Third and his companions. Just like the PetRok Islands where leisure and storytelling rule, this coin celebrates humor, relaxation, and imagination. It’s not just a token—it’s a lifestyle that rewards those who embrace fun, creativity, and the spirit of collective adventure.
